summary: Adds a door to the east tower of castle volkhanier that leads to the balcony
descriptionHtml:
Door_To_Valerica\'s_Study: By TailAbNormal 

What It Does: Adds an entrance/exit to the Volkhanier castle balcony connected
to the castles east tower.
   You need a key (located on the ground of the balcony near the new door) to 
open the entrance. 

Bugs: For some reason, entering the balcony through the east tower door will 
teleport you to the ground below the balcony. 
   I have no Idea what is causing this
but It only seems to happen once, so If it does, just TCL back up and save the 
game and it shouldn\'t happen again.
author: TailAbNormal
